<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c4">[اللِّحاف]</span>: ما يلتحف به.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c4">[م]</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c4">[اللِّحام]</span>: جمع: لحم.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c5">واللِّحام:</span> ما يلحم به الصدع من ذهب أو فضة ونحوهما.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>